sources.title: I giganti della Tessaglia (1960)
sources.description: In order to placate the angry gods, who have allowed Thessaly to be overrun with barbarian invaders and beset with natural disasters, King Jason takes his Argonauts on a search for the fabled Golden Fleece. Meanwhile, back at home, his scheming regent is plotting to get his hands on the kingdom--and the queen. Watch on RetroFlix:Â  https://retroflix.org/i-giganti-della-tessaglia-1960/
